@node History "MyLang · History"

@{b}1.5@{ub} (22.09.2002)
________________

· new way of defining multiple translations (see documentation for details)

· stack is expanded when necessary

· fixed default tools in docs' tooltypes

· semicolon can be used as comment marker

· slightly changed user interface

· added search function to the vocabulary editor

· number of all words in the dictionary is also displayed during the session

· new option: program now asks before it cancells unfinished session

· new option: requester can be popped to emphasize correct answer

· fixed: program crashed if some dictionary lines were too long



@{b}1.4@{ub} (30.05.2002)
________________

· sound support added

· elapsed time indicator added

· percentage score is displayed again



@{b}1.3@{ub} (18.01.2002)
________________

· locale support added again

· stats window rewritten from scratch (see documentation for details)

· some minor bugs fixed



@{b}1.2@{ub} (12.10.2001)
________________

· added internal editor for vocabulary files

· new preferences system - now uses own Preferences window

· lots of internal improvements

· locale support removed (sorry, although it'll be back soon)



@{b}1.1@{ub} (15.09.2001)
________________

· rewrote options/vocabulary parser so spaces and quotes are allowed

· languages names are now defined in vocabulary files (instead of options)

· first Aminet release



@{b}1.0@{ub} (13.08.2001)
________________

· first personal release (few people saw it)

@endnode

